	Sandra lip lock    
	 London, Jan. 21 (PTI): Actress Sandra Bullock loved locking lips with Meryl Streep at the Critics Choice Movie Awards and now hopes they can kiss again, this time on the big screen.      
	Bullock and Streep embraced and kissed as they shared the best actress award after staging a mock stand-off.      
	Bullock admits that kissing Streep was a career highlight, reports The Sun. It was mind blowing, said Bullock.      
	She joked that the two of them are looking to play lesbians in a film. We may do a movie together that has a little Sapphic element to it. Everyones been like: Lets get them together as lovers, said Bullock.
                                                                                                                                                      
